Class ClearableRegistry<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraftforge.registries.ClearableRegistry<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<V>, IObjectIntIterable<V>, IRegistry<V>

    public class ClearableRegistry<V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRegistry<V>
    A IRegistry implementation that allows for removing of objects. This is a internal helper class used by Forge for managing things that reset during Server initialization.
